    "Furthermore, automation in ASFRs reduces the need for constant human oversight, lowering operational costs and minimizing the risk of human errors.",
    "A schematic representation of ASFR is provided in Figure 5a.A self-optimizing microreactor system has been devised specifically for closed-loop optimization of the Heck reaction, employing a \"black-box\" optimization strategy directed by Nelder-Mead simplex method algorithm [57].",
